{"tid":1056683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺自殺變成左香港唯一有效既申訴方式?","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T10:24:44.000Z","uid":123264,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fce421153ec5643c002a338ada1b72a073a51426","tid":1056683,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:13:07.000Z","msg":"係公司比老闆恰 比人歧視 比人排<br />\n呢d野同屋企人 同事 朋友講 好多人都會叫你 「忍下啦 係咁架啦」<br />\n識得分清事非既人只佔少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放上黎討論區 仲有人可能會屌番你轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之香港人就係叫你忍忍忍忍忍忍忍忍忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 永遠唔覺真係仆街果個有錯 永遠係覺得你唔捱得 永遠唔會覺得你真係好辛苦好想死<br />\n永遠係要人地比人折磨到跳樓死撚左之後 先肯認人地係痛苦緊 永遠要等人地死撚左之後先相信受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係幾時開始 香港人會覺得受苦 受排斥 呢種事情係正常? 點解我地會有呢種「所有人都要受苦受排斥抵撚你死」咁撚扭曲既心態???<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315537e5673404b47c74d77235caa3c468e59fdb","tid":1056683,"uid":91813,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"弱肉強食"},{"pid":"87c1cccad136fff4b922b98ef998036b5d954c4b","tid":1056683,"uid":184502,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"最慘係自殺都未必有效申訴"},{"pid":"d194cfafd72a6097c55ee707ee1670745b0fb7d5","tid":1056683,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c1cccad136fff4b922b98ef998036b5d954c4b","tid":1056683,"uid":184502,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"最慘係自殺都未必有效申訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"c83c2a3057e4b3481b2acbd1e9d1e71921c5ba31","tid":1056683,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"戇居，死無對證"},{"pid":"9ddbdf6225a8369bbf36100ca00503da81ee0459","tid":1056683,"uid